+# Coordination Log
+
+Use this file to share decisions, status updates, and context with other agents.
+Write your updates below. There is no enforced format — use whatever structure helps.
+
+---
+
+## Analytics Dashboard API — Completed
+
+**What was done:**
+- Created `src/models/analytics.ts` with three interfaces: `AnalyticsSummary`, `UserAnalytics`, `TrendPoint`
+- Created `src/services/analytics.service.ts` with `AnalyticsService` class using constructor DI (takes `UserRepository` and `OrderRepository`)
+  - `getSummary()` — aggregates totalUsers, totalOrders, revenue, activeUsers
+  - `getUserAnalytics(userId)` — per-user order count, total spent, last active date
+  - `getTrends(metric, startDate, endDate)` — daily time-series bucketing for 'revenue' and 'orders' metrics
+- Created `tests/services/analytics.service.test.ts` with 10 tests covering all methods and edge cases
+
+**Key decisions:**
+- "Active users" defined as users who have at least one order (matches typical analytics semantics)
+- `lastActive` falls back to `user.createdAt` when user has no orders
+- Metric validation happens upfront in `getTrends` (before iterating orders) so unknown metrics always throw
+- Trends are bucketed by day (ISO date string) and sorted chronologically
+
